app_standard.noteCN:
- 修改应用名称为数据滤镜，旧版本1.3以下已经废弃
- 添加测试菜单，点击右上角打开
- 修复Android7以下崩溃问题
- 修复动态代理问题
- 修复Android11读取apk路径问题
- 模拟器下载x86版本，手机下载arm版本
app_standard.noteEN:
- Modify the application name to Data Filter. The old version below 1.3 has been deprecated.
- Add the test menu and click on the upper right corner to open
- Fix the crash problem below Android7
- Fix the dynamic proxy problem
- Fix the Android11 read apk path Problem
- Download the x86 version for the emulator and the arm version for the mobile phone
